## for each language [/github/languages/{languageName}?order_by={orderbyName}&limit={limitNumber}]

### List All GitHub for each language [GET]

+ Parameters
    + order_by (string) - 
        github_id
        stargazers_count
        forks_count
        commit_created_at
        commit_updated_at
        owner_id
        owner_followers
        owner_following
        owner_created_at
        owner_updated_at
        
    + limit (number) - 
    get repositories count (1 - 50)
    
